SECTION 8: ACKNOWLEDGEMENT

GaiaThinker was built on the traditional,
ancestral, and unceded territories of the
Coast Salish peoples, including the Qayqayt,
Kwikwetlem, and Stó:lō Nations.

We are grateful to the Indigenous fire keepers,
educators, environmental scientists, and community
members whose knowledge and stories are at the
heart of this platform.

